title: This week in Parliament: 12 to 16 October 2015 (New Zealand Parliament)
text: ( Source : New Zealand Parliament ) After question time on Tuesday, 13 October , the House is expected to begin the first readings of a number of Government bills, including the Environment Canterbury ( Transitional Governance Arrangements)
